('Riker, Maryann J', 'Changeling', '-', 'M. Riker', '-', 'Phillipsburg, N.J', 'Maryann Riker', '2006', 'Mixed media artist''s sculpture; one-of-a-kind. A cabinet-shaped structure with two illustrated panels (moon, tape measure, butterfly). These unfold and reveal an intimate interior.  Collage on exterior and interior walls; interior contains mirrors on each panel, plus one shelf with mounted seashell. A third mirror and second seashell stand inside the slotted cabinet', '-', '-', '-', '-', '-', '-', 'Riker, Maryann J', '-', 'Artists'' books|Metamorphosis in art', '-', '-', '-', '-', '-', '-', 'Artists'' books|Miniature books', '-', '-', '1 cabinet-shaped sculpture', '080131s2006    njunnn            aneng d', 'specol_N7433_4_R543_C43_2006');
